Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:17.89,Campus Common,美鈴,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:17.89,Campus Common,美鈴,0,0,0,,それが、わたしにとっての\n最善なんです。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:21.70,Campus Common,美鈴,0,0,0,,
